4962.description:
Fukuhara Kouta is a college student who has bad luck that causes problems everywhere he goes. One day, he runs into Shinomiya Naoya, a fellow student with the opposite problem - super good luck. Shinomiya decides to help him out. Now, in order to divide the luck between them, they need to be with each other all the time. 

(Source: MyDramaList)

~~ Adapted from the manga &quot;Fukou-kun wa Kiss Suru Shika Nai!&quot;

5362.description:
&quot;I want to grow up quicker, so I can date Minato-san.&quot;

Minato Akira inherited his grandfather's coin laundry. And so, the middle-aged former corporate drone, Akira, peacefully ran the well-loved coin laundry. One day, a high-school student, Katsuki Shintaro, enters the coin laundry. Despite the difference in age, they quickly became friends. However, Shintaro suddenly finds out that Akira is gay.

(Source: Mangaupdates)

~~ Adapted from the manga &quot;Minato Shouji Coin Laundry&quot;
